'''阿瓊主戰坦克'''簡稱'''阿瓊坦克'''。是印度研发的国产主战坦克，名称“阿琼”来源于印度史诗[[摩诃婆罗多|摩诃婆罗多]]中人物'''[[阿周那|阿周那]]'''（Arjuna）。

==發展沿革==
印度国防部于1972年将研发任务下达给战斗车辆研发中心，<ref name="Smith" />1984年3月，在耗費了三億盧比的研製資金後，印度[[戰車|戰車]]研發局研製出兩輛樣車。到1988年初印度戰車研發局研製出10輛樣車。1996年印度政府决定在阿瓦迪的战车工厂开始量产该坦克。<ref name="globsec-arjun">[http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/arjun.htm Arjun] {{Wayback|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/arjun.htm |date=20081022161931 }} globalsecurity.com</ref><ref name="elephant" />2007年印度現任國防部長認為阿瓊已經可以投入實戰，並完成所需演習科目；2011年3月宣布阿琼坦克改进型阿琼MK2的研发工作告成。与阿琼基础型相比，改良型的国产率达90%，增加了多达93项改进，其中包括13项大改，改进后可用发射[[以色列|以色列]]製炮射导弹。尽管最初的时候有多达一半的部件是进口的，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://164.100.47.5/newdebate/214/22102008/11.00amTo12.00Noon.pdf |title=Microsoft Word - 22-10 i.rtf |format=PDF |accessdate=2014-02-10 |archive-date=2011-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110529070506/http://164.100.47.5/newdebate/214/22102008/11.00amTo12.00Noon.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>到后来印度逐渐地在用国产货取代进口货<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/LAND-FORCES/Equipment/Armour/42-Arjun.html |title=Land Forces Site - Arjun |publisher=Bharat Rakshak |date=7 March 2001 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111018132944/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/LAND-FORCES/Equipment/Armour/42-Arjun.html |archivedate=2011-10-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.drdo.gov.in/drdo/labs/ARDE/English/index.jsp?pg=achieve.jsp |title=ARDE Achievements |publisher=Drdo.gov.in |date=22 July 2010 |accessdate=10 June 2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721155632/http://www.drdo.gov.in/drdo/labs/ARDE/English/index.jsp?pg=achieve.jsp |archivedate=2011-07-21|deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但到實際生産中，進口部件比例高達60％。<ref>http://news.xinhuanet.com/mil/2009-06/22/content_11582996.html{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} 新華網:從驕傲到悲哀——印度“阿瓊”主戰坦克</ref>阿琼研发拖延时间过长一个重要原因是军方的要求总是随时间推移提高，如1974年五月政府一开始要求限制费用为{{INRConvert|155|m|1}}，<ref name="Smith">{{cite book |last=Smith |first=Chris|title=India's Ad hoc Arsenal: Direction or Drift in Defence Policy?|url=http://books.google.com/?id=wirzhu5EaqAC&printsec=frontcover&dq=India+MBT+production#PPA149,M1|accessdate=23 April 2008 |publisher= Sipri |isbn= 978-0-19-829168-8 |pages=148–151|year=1994 }}</ref>1995年由于设计不断推倒重来和通货膨胀已花了{{INRConvert|3|b|1}}。<ref name="May2008PIB">{{cite press release |title= Arjun Battle Tank |url= http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=38445&kwd= |publisher= Government of India |date= 5 May 2008 |access-date= 2014-02-10 |archive-date= 2009-05-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090511013350/http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=38445&kwd= |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2010年，印度将阿琼和T-90进行了越野和射击对比测试，得出的报告表明阿琼的越野和火控性能更为先进。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Shukla |first1=Ajai |title=Arjun tank outruns, outguns Russian T-90 |url=http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/arjun-tank-outruns-outguns-russian-t-90/389650/ |website=Business Standard India |accessdate=2019-05-26 |date=2010-03-25 |archive-date=2010-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326223421/http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/arjun-tank-outruns-outguns-russian-t-90/389650/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=61870 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612095904/http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=61870 |archive-date=2010-06-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==部署==
2000年印军订购124辆,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.indiamart.com/news-analysis/indian-army-to-recei-15582.html |title=Indian Army to receive 124 Arjun tanks by 2009,Security Issues, News Analysis, India News Online |publisher=News.indiamart.com |date=14 May 2007 |accessdate=2010-02-07}}{{dead link|date=September 2011}}</ref>预计花费4亿7千1百万美元。<ref name="FI">{{cite web |last=India |first=Frontier |url=http://frontierindia.net/indian-mod-outlines-roadmap-for-mbt-arjun-mark-ii-in-pipeline |title=Indian MoD outlines roadmap for MBT Arjun, Mark II in pipeline | Frontier India Strategic and Defence - News, Analysis, Opinion |publisher=Frontierindia.net |date= |accessdate=2010-02-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212095722/http://frontierindia.net/indian-mod-outlines-roadmap-for-mbt-arjun-mark-ii-in-pipeline |archivedate=2010年2月12日 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>预发展型的阿琼部署在43坦克团并在2001年国庆阅兵时露过面。<ref name="RDPArade2001">{{cite web |url=http://mod.nic.in/samachar/16feb01/html/mart.htm |title=Arms and the Men on Rajpath |author=Chandra Mohan, A. |date=Sainik Samachar |work=16 Feb 2001 |publisher=Ministry of DEfence, India |accessdate=2011-12-02|deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100726220901/http://mod.nic.in/samachar/16feb01/html/mart.htm |archivedate=2010-07-26 }}</ref>
第一批生产型16辆于2004年服役。<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=2c989f63-5120-4d94-9d36-868a28d3b7d3 "Arjun rumbles to life, Army raises maiden regiment"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=2c989f63-5120-4d94-9d36-868a28d3b7d3 |date=20190713152301 }} Hindustan Times,  26 May 2009</ref>该团于2009年5月25日部署了45辆该坦克成为印军首个全阿琼的坦克团。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.janes.com/defence/land_forces/news/jdw/jdw050921_1_n.shtml | title = System failures stall Arjun trials | publisher = [[Jane's_Information_Group|Jane's Information Group]] | date = 21 September 2005 | first = Rahul | last = Bedi | accessdate = 2008-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080208220743/http://www.janes.com/defence/land_forces/news/jdw/jdw050921_1_n.shtml | archivedate =2008-02-08| deadurl = yes }}{{subscription}}</ref> 陆军在2010年5月追加了124辆MK-I的订单，8月追加了124辆MK-II的订单。<ref name="arjun_second_order">{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/India/Army-places-fresh-order-for-124-more-Arjun-tanks/articleshow/5940228.cms|publisher=Times of India|title=Army places fresh order for 124 more Arjun tanks|date=17 May 2010|accessdate=2012-08-11|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607152026/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/India/Army-places-fresh-order-for-124-more-Arjun-tanks/articleshow/5940228.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/army-to-purchase-more-arjun-tanks/391862/ |title=Army to purchase more Arjun tanks |publisher=Business-standard.com |date= |accessdate=2010-05-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100614202523/http://www.business-standard.com/india/news/army-to-purchase-more-arjun-tanks/391862/ |archivedate=2010-06-14|deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.upi.com/Business_News/Security-Industry/2010/05/21/Future-of-Indias-Arjun-tank-looks-secure/UPI-94101274452185/ |title=Future of India's Arjun tank looks secure |publisher=UPI.com |date=21 May 2010 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100707160517/http://www.upi.com/Business_News/Security-Industry/2010/05/21/Future-of-Indias-Arjun-tank-looks-secure/UPI-94101274452185 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
2011年6月超过1百辆阿琼已经交给印陆军<ref>{{citation |url=http://drdo.gov.in/drdo/pub/techfocus/2011/tf_june2011.pdf |title=Technology focus |format=PDF |volume=19 |number=3 |date=June 2011 |publisher=DRDO |accessdate=2011-06-10 |issn=0971-4413 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809042539/http://drdo.gov.in/drdo/pub/techfocus/2011/tf_june2011.pdf |archive-date=2011-08-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>最新一个全装备阿琼的坦克团是75团，该团一直都沿用老旧的T-55。

美《防务新闻》周刊网站2015年5月8日报道，印度陆军军官证实，印度大部分自制“阿琼”MK1主战坦克已经被停驶，因其技术故障和难以进口部分零件。
“陆军所有124辆这种坦克里有75%已经不能用了，”这位军官说。

==自製裝甲==
[[File:Arjun_MBT_bump_track_test.JPG|thumb]]
[[File:Leopard_2A4_Austria_1.JPG|thumb]]
印度為“阿瓊”專門研製了一種新型[[複合裝甲|複合裝甲]]，號稱性能直逼[[英國|英國]]“喬巴姆”裝甲。称为坎昌（Kanchan）陶瓷複合裝甲，並可外掛反應裝甲，這些特種裝甲均由位於印度海德拉巴市的“國防冶金研究所” （Defence Metallurgical Laboratory—DML）研製（該研究所以前還曾研製過用於改進[[T-72|T-72M1]]的“賈卡爾”複合裝甲），而總體防護等研究則由“[[終點彈道研究院|終點彈道研究院]]” （Terminal Ballistic Research Loboratary—TBRL）承擔。

炮塔正面兩側各有一塊體積比較大的複合裝甲塊，裝置類似於[[日本|日本]][[90式戰車|90式戰車]]，但是其厚度明顯更大（大約有800—900毫米），預計該複合裝甲也是按模組化思想設計的，可方便地更換或升級。車側面前3個負重輪處裙板用附加裝甲加強。
